channel.description:
[center][size=12pt][u][b]508 Command Generator[/b][/u] By: Davidi2[/size][/center]
Well I've been looking around and have noticed a lot of 317 command generators, but none for any other cache version. So I decided to make one myself.
V2 UPDATES:
[ul][li]~Animation Option[/li] [li]~GFX Option[/li] [li]~"Do to all players" option[/li][/ul]
[hr] [b]CREDITS:[/b]
[ul][li]Me, for programming, designing, and developing the program[/li]
[li][b]Ideas:[list] [li]Explisionist- GFX, Animations (V2)[/li] [li]...[/li] [li]...[/li][li]...[/li] [/list][/ul]
[hr] [b]Current Problems:[/b]
[ul][li]Only works with Bulby bases, or sources that use frames.java for sending messages ect.[/li] [li]Very limited features (see below!)[/li][/ul]
This program is very self-explanatory, but if you need help just post.
V1: [img]http://img692.imageshack.us/img692/3505/508cg.png[/img]
V2: [img]http://img510.imageshack.us/img510/8228/63453203.png[/img] I need suggestions for more features! Just post them here and I will (probably) use them, and put your name on the ideas list!
DOWNLOAD URL: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?zm2tnynxzdz]Download V2 -Fixed[/url]
